PN,30601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FCancer cases have reached a record
OL,7,Flevel in the UK, with one charity
OL,8,Fwarning that NHS services are
OL,9,Fstruggling to cope with a rising
OL,10,Fdemand for treatment.
OL,12,FAnalysis by Cancer Research UK shows
OL,13,Fmore than 403,000 people are diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith the disease in the country every
OL,15,Fyear ` or around one person every 80
OL,16,Fseconds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FThis is largely due to a growing and
OL,7,Fageing population, as people are more
OL,8,Flikely to develop cancer as they get
OL,9,Folder, although previous research
OL,10,Fsuggests bowel cancer diagnoses are
OL,11,Frising sharply among younger adults.
OL,13,FIn its new Cancer in the UK Report
OL,14,F2026, Cancer Research says incidences
OL,15,Fof all types of cancer have risen from
OL,16,F620 per 100,000 people in a decade
OL,17,F(from 610).
OL,19,FMeanwhile, cases diagnosed at an early
OL,20,Fstage have barely changed, rising from
OL,21,F54% to 55%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FThe report said the rise in incidence
OL,7,Ftrends is partly reflected by
OL,8,Fincreasing levels of obesity, which
OL,9,Fpushes up the risk of cancer.
OL,11,FDeath rates have fallen and the
OL,12,Fproportion of people surviving a
OL,13,Fdecade or more after diagnosis has
OL,14,Frisen, but Cancer Research UK said
OL,15,Fthis progress is at risk of stalling,
OL,16,Fin part due to pressure on cancer
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FIt adds that cancer waiting times
OL,7,Facross the UK are among the worst on
OL,8,Frecord, and that NHS services are
OL,9,Fstruggling to cope with rising demand.
OL,11,FThe charity said the government's
OL,12,Frecently published National Cancer
OL,13,FPlan for England is a "crucial step"
OL,14,Ftowards improving care, but there
OL,15,Fneeds to be "funding and resources to
OL,16,Ftranslate ambition into impact".
OL,18,FCancer Research UK chief executive
OL,19,FMichelle Mitchell said: "More people
OL,20,Fare being diagnosed with cancer than
OL,21,Fever before.
OL,26,@uD@WOUuD@dO]wD@MOUxD@_O]{D@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,F"Although cancer survival has doubled
OL,7,Fsince the 1970s, progress has slowed
OL,8,Fover the last decade.
OL,10,F"The UK government's recently
OL,11,Fpublished National Cancer Plan for
OL,12,FEngland could make a big difference,
OL,13,Fbut only if it turns into improvements
OL,14,Ffor cancer patients.
OL,16,F"Publishing the plan is not a 'job
OL,17,Fdone' on cancer: ambitions to diagnose
OL,18,Fcancers earlier, meet cancer wait
OL,19,Ftargets and improve best practice
OL,20,Ftreatment must happen quickly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FThe charity wants screening programmes
OL,7,Fsuch as for lung cancer to be rolled
OL,8,Fout widely and effectively and the
OL,9,Frollout of innovative cancer tests to
OL,10,Fbe accelerated.
OL,12,FAround 107,000 cancer patients were
OL,13,Fwaiting more than 62 days to start
OL,14,Ftreatment across the UK in 2025, it
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,FCancer Research UK praised the
OL,7,FGovernment's commitments to meet
OL,8,Fwaiting times targets in England but
OL,9,Fsaid the situation is much worse in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and called for more
OL,11,Finvestment nationwide in specialist
OL,12,Fstaff and equipment.
OL,14,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We have delivered
OL,16,Fa record number of diagnostic tests in
OL,17,Fthe last 12 months, backed by an extra
OL,18,F#26 billion for the NHS.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
