OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,F"And the number of patients getting a
OL,7,Fcancer diagnosis or all-clear on time
OL,8,Fis the highest in five years ` but we
OL,9,Fare not complacent.
OL,11,F"Our National Cancer Plan sets out how
OL,12,Fpatients will receive a diagnosis
OL,13,Ffaster, treatment sooner and better
OL,14,Fsupport to live well with cancer, with
OL,15,Fthe aim of 75% of patients diagnosed
OL,16,Ffrom 2035 to be cancer-free or living
OL,17,Fwell after five years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
