PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,F"Our historic Tobacco and Vapes Bill,
OL,7,Fwhich is due to come into law soon,
OL,8,Fwill also protect future generations
OL,9,Ffrom cancer."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHead of data and evidence at Prostate
OL,17,FCancer UK, Natalia Norori, said:
OL,18,F"Cancer diagnoses are rising, and as
OL,19,Fthe UK's most common cancer, with
OL,20,F64,000 new cases each year, prostate
OL,21,Fcancer plays a big part in this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,F"The good news is that prostate cancer
OL,7,Fis highly treatable when caught early.
OL,8,FBut with more than 1,000,000 men set
OL,9,Fto be living with the disease by 2040,
OL,10,Fearly detection needs to be a priority
OL,11,Fif we're serious about saving lives."
OL,13,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "Latest data
OL,14,Fshows that early diagnosis in England
OL,15,Fis at a record high and is continuing
OL,16,Fto rise, with staff also now
OL,17,Fdelivering 30% more cancer checks than
OL,18,Fin 2021 ` ensuring survival is also at
OL,19,Fan all-time high.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]uD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776942175
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record high in UK
OL,4,Cwith diagnosis every 80 seconds
OL,6,F"But we know we need to go further to
OL,7,Fdiagnose more cancers earlier and save
OL,8,Fmore lives, which is why the National
OL,9,FCancer Plan will transform services to
OL,10,Fspeed up diagnosis, cut waits and
OL,11,Fimprove care for anyone affected."
